title: North Korea says no U.S. talks planned at Olympics
text:
North Korea says no U.S. talks planned at Olympics 7:26am IST - 01:25 
State media says North Korea has no intention of meeting U.S. officials during the Winter Olympics, shutting down hopes the Games may resolve a standoff over the North's nuclear program ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
